FBIS3-36589 "drsov026_m_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-026 Document Type:Daily Report 8 Feb 1994 Tajikistan Armed Afghan Militants Clash With Border Guards LD0802112694 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0952 GMT 8 Feb 94 LD0802112694 Moscow ITAR-TASS Language: English Article Type:BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Sergey Ostanin] [Text] Moscow February 8 TASS -- Around 30 armed militants made an attempt to illegally cross from Afghanistan into Tajikistan on Monday night, in the area of the 12th Pyandzh border guard post controlled by Russian border guards, ITAR-TASS learned on Tuesday [8 February] from the press-service of Russian border guard troops. The militants seized one of Tajik islands on the Pyandzh river. Their positions came under fire opened by the Tajik side, afterwards, the militants retreated to the adjoining territory, the same source said.
